# Metadata Modeling

- Treat metadata as a versioned product surface, not a side effect.
- Keep `DatasetDefinition` stable across `DatasetInstance` periods.
- Apply edits through draft -> preview -> publish workflows.
- Do not silently change field identities or level mappings.
- Require explicit migration policy when data types change.
